OL,7,FMerseyside police say more drug
OL,8,Fdrivers than drink drivers were
OL,9,Farrested over the festive period.
OL,11,FOfficers arrested the most drug
OL,12,Fdrivers of any force during a national
OL,13,Fcrackdown. Police caught 469 drivers
OL,14,Funder the influence of drugs in
OL,15,FDecember as part of a national
OL,16,Fcrackdown - more than any other police
OL,17,Fforce in the UK.
