OL,3,CMerseyside Police arrested more drug
OL,4,Cdrivers than anywhere else in the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FOp Limit, is a drink and drug drive
OL,8,Fcampaign that takes place over the
OL,9,Ffestive period and brings together all
OL,10,Fpolice forces in a concerted effort to
OL,11,Fremove dangerous drivers from our
OL,12,Froads.
OL,14,FIn January, Merseyside Police revealed
OL,15,Fthey arrested 469 drug drivers and 191
OL,16,Fdrink drivers from 20 November 2023 to
OL,17,F1 January 2024.
