OL,7,FTo help tackle drug driving in
OL,8,FMerseyside, Roads Policing Chief
OL,9,FInspector, Stuart McIver, believes the
OL,10,Fstigma surrounding drink driving now
OL,11,Fneeds to be applied to drug driving.
OL,13,FHe said: "The number of people who we
OL,14,Fhave witnessed driving whilst under
OL,15,Fthe influence of drugs in Merseyside
OL,16,Fis simply staggering.
