OL,3,CMerseyside Police arrested more drug
OL,4,Cdrivers than anywhere else in the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,F"All the stigma and shame that goes
OL,8,Fwith drink driving absolutely also
OL,9,Fneeds to apply to drug driving. The
OL,10,F469 people we arrested for drug
OL,11,Fdriving during Op Limit could have
OL,12,Fcalled a taxi, got a lift, used public
OL,13,Ftransport or stayed at home, but sadly
OL,14,Fthey didn't. They arrogantly put their
OL,15,Fown convenience above the safety of
OL,16,Feveryone else in Merseyside.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
