OL,3,CMerseyside Police arrested more drug
OL,4,Cdrivers than anywhere else in the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,F"As a force, we were an early adopter
OL,8,Fof roadside drug wipes as a tool for
OL,9,Fcrime detection and prevention and
OL,10,Fit's an area we've heavily invested
OL,11,Fin. Using the roadside drug wipes so
OL,12,Ffrequently has given us a unique
OL,13,Finsight into the scale of the problem
OL,14,Fof drug driving.
OL,16,F"The number of drug driving offenders
OL,17,Fwe caught across the six weeks of
OL,18,FOperation Limit gives you an idea of
OL,19,Fthe true scale of this problem. We
OL,20,Fhave an epidemic of drug driving that
OL,21,Fwe need to tackle."
