OL,7,FAlthough Operation Limit concluded in
OL,8,FJanuary, Merseyside Police will
OL,9,Fcontinue to take a robust approach to
OL,10,Fdrink and drug driving throughout the
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FChief Insp McIver added: "This year's
OL,14,FOperation Limit might have finished `
OL,15,Fbut we haven't finished tackling drug
OL,16,Fdriving. It's not acceptable, it will
OL,17,Fnot be tolerated, and we will be
OL,18,Fcracking down on this all year round.
OL,26,@uD@ZOU
