OL,7,F"Sadly last year we saw an increase in
OL,8,Fserious injuries and fatalities in
OL,9,FMerseyside and drink and drug driving
OL,10,Fis responsible for many of these
OL,11,Fincidents every year. Innocent lives
OL,12,Fhave been taken and families left
OL,13,Fshattered because of the selfish
OL,14,Factions of some drivers.
