OL,7,F"My message to those who choose to
OL,8,Fdrive whilst under the influence is
OL,9,Fthis: you are not only putting your
OL,10,Fown life and your own future at risk,
OL,11,Fbut also the lives of innocent people.
OL,12,FIs it really worth risking your own
OL,13,Flife and the lives others?"
OL,15,FIf you know or suspect someone is
OL,16,Fdriving whilst under the influence of
OL,17,Falcohol or drugs, then please contact
OL,18,F@MerPolCC, 101, the Roads Policing
OL,19,FUnit on 0151 777 5747 or Crimestoppers
OL,20,Fanonymously on 0800 555 111.
